videos.headline: Arkansas' Boyd dives for TD
videos.description: Rakeem Boyd puts Arkansas on the board with a diving 5-yard touchdown through the Vanderbilt defense.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Vaughn breaks out for 63-yard TD run
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaugh takes off for a massive 63-yard touchdown run for the Commodores.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Williams comes up with INT
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Joejuan Williams jumps the pass and comes up with the interception and returns it to Arkansas territory.

videos.headline: Shurmur finds Pinkney in the corner for Vanderbilt TD
videos.description: The Commodores run the play fake and Kyle Shurmur connects with a wide-open Jared Pinkney to put Vanderbilt on top of Arkansas 14-7.

videos.headline: Hayden jets 38 yards for Arkansas TD
videos.description: Chase Hayden takes off up the middle unopposed for a 38-yard Arkansas touchdown, tying the game with Vanderbilt at 14.

videos.headline: Shurmur and Pinkney connect again for 40-yard TD
videos.description: Jared Pinkney comes down with a bobbled pass and dives for a 40-yard Vanderbilt touchdown.

videos.headline: Vaughn notches second rushing TD for Vanderbilt
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaughn fights his way 11 yards for the Vanderbilt touchdown to extend its lead over Arkansas.

videos.headline: Arkansas' Storey connects with Morris for 11-yard TD
videos.description: Ty Storey finds Tyson Morris in the back of the end zone for an Arkansas touchdown.

videos.headline: Vaughn rushes for third TD vs. Arkansas
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaughn dives in for his third rushing touchdown of the day for Vanderbilt against Arkansas.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt big man comes up with unreal bobbling INT
videos.description: Louis Vecchio bobbles the ball a few times before pinning it against his helmet for a Vanderbilt interception.

videos.headline: Blasingame powers in for 5-yard Vanderbilt TD
videos.description: Khari Blasingame muscles his way in for the touchdown putting Vanderbilt on top of Arkansas 45-24.

videos.headline: Storey connects with O'Grady for Arkansas TD
videos.description: Ty Storey connects with a leaping Cheyenne O'Grady in the corner of the end zone for the 12-yard Arkansas touchdown.
